Uses of Class
model.Student

Packages that use Student
Package
Description
Assignment
Contains two classes, MainApp and Database, to upload the data files for Student, Faculty, FYP Coordinator and Project lists and start the Final Year Project application.
controller
Contains all the necessary classes to manage the information between the view clases and the model classes.
model
Contains all the User classes such as Student, Faculty and FYP Coordinator; the Request classes such as Student to Faculty, Student to FYP Coordinator, and Faculty to FYP Coordinator; and finally the Project class.
